QueryText: how to control fruit & shoot borer of brinjal?
KCCAns: Remove the affected terminal shoot showing boreholes. Remove the affected fruits and destroy. Spray any one of the following chemicals starting from one month after planting at 15 days interval. 1. Carbaryl 50 WP 2 g/lit + Wettable Sulphur 50% WP 2 g/lit (or) 2. Neem oil 3 % (or)  3. Quinalphos 25 EC 2 ml/lit + Neem oil 3 % (or) 4. Neem Seed Kernel Extract 5 % (or) 5. Avoid using synthetic Pyrethroids.
